pull_request.title: Change return value of `USING_TIME_RATHER_THAN_CYCLES` to unsigned int.
pull_request.body:
Resolves issue #776 when attempting to build for arm64-v8a in clang.

Would also like advice on whether `_bench_init_perfcounters` parameters and local variables should be unsigned, as it would make sense to fix them here.

pull_request.title: Integrated picnic v3.0
pull_request.body:
Integrates picnic v3.0.
* Implement new Picnic 3 parameter set. This implementation replaces the Picnic 2 parameter set.
* Implement new Picnic instances with full Sbox layer.
* Various small improvements and bug fixes.
* Remove all optimizations for partial LowMC instances except for OLLE.
